</dl>
<ul>
<li><a href="/wiki/Pete_Overend_Watts" title="Pete Overend Watts">Pete Overend Watts</a> – bass guitar, vocals, guitar <small>(1969–1980, 2009, 2013)</small></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Ian_Hunter_(singer)" title="Ian Hunter (singer)">Ian Hunter</a> – vocals, guitar, piano, bass guitar <small>(1969–1974, 2009, 2013)</small></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Mick_Ralphs" title="Mick Ralphs">Mick Ralphs</a> – guitar, vocals, keyboards <small>(1969–1973, 2009, 2013)</small></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Verden_Allen" title="Verden Allen">Verden Allen</a> – <a href="/wiki/Hammond_organ" title="Hammond organ">organ</a>, backing vocals <small>(1969–1972, 2009, 2013)</small></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Dale_Griffin" title="Dale Griffin">Dale "Buffin" Griffin</a> – drums, backing vocals, percussion <small>(1969–1980, 2009)</small></li>
</ul>
<dl>
<dt>Former members</dt>
</dl>
<ul>
<li><a href="/wiki/Morgan_Fisher" title="Morgan Fisher">Morgan Fisher</a> – keyboards, backing vocals <small>(1972–1980)</small></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Luther_Grosvenor" title="Luther Grosvenor">Ariel Bender</a> – guitar, backing vocals <small>(1973–1974)</small></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Mick_Ronson" title="Mick Ronson">Mick Ronson</a> – guitar, backing vocals <small>(1974 died 1993)</small></li>
<li>Ray Major - guitar, vocals <small>(1974-1980 "Drive On, Shouting and Pointing")</small></li>
<li>Nigel Benjamin - voice, guitar <small>(1974-1976)"Drive On, Shouting and Pointing")</small></li>
<li>Steve Hyams - guitar, vocals <small>(1977; died 2013)</small></li>
</ul>
